an&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;而你領展就啪啪打政府臉, 潑冷水, 分拆去香港對手, 新加坡上市!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;呢個已經會一大罪, 不單對香港人唔住. 對國家背叛&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31950123&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1586594016684599b74c67d4_45390442"/><published>2025-06-08T09:29:09+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f46dcc490211cb8c33af69f128da9418</id><title>ETF 最好</title><updated>2025-06-08T09:43:21+08:00</updated><author><name>奇幻的pizza</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-08T09:43:21+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572744756"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572744756"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finvestment%2F3462517%2F%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E8%259D%2595%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%258B%25BF%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E6%259D%258E%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%259A%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258E%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259C%25ACETF%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2599%25BA&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=df616568e1c8871d804fb866c6197581&amp;amp;fid=57" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.stheadline.com/inves ... 理專業性-李聲揚簡單低成本ETF更明智&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31950134&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3